274
00:19:19,367 --> 00:19:21,619
But my team has not made
such recommendations,

275
00:19:21,702 --> 00:19:24,372
and we haven't had
any customer complaints about it either.

276
00:19:25,164 --> 00:19:28,709
But if Team 1 has in fact done that,

277
00:19:28,793 --> 00:19:31,337
then we'll step in
and help out as much as we can

278
00:19:31,420 --> 00:19:32,505
to get it sorted--

279
00:19:33,172 --> 00:19:34,882
Sorry to cut you off, Jin-woo.

280
00:19:34,965 --> 00:19:38,386
I appreciate your concern for my team.

281
00:19:38,469 --> 00:19:41,263
But we're still figuring out
the exact situation,

282
00:19:41,347 --> 00:19:45,309
so let's save the hypotheticals for now
rather than rushing in, shall we?

283
00:19:46,644 --> 00:19:47,520
I'm sorry, Mr. Kim.

284
00:19:47,603 --> 00:19:48,604
Anyone else?

285
00:19:48,688 --> 00:19:51,607
Anyone from my team?

286
00:19:53,275 --> 00:19:54,652
For now,

287
00:19:55,945 --> 00:19:59,115
maybe we should pass this
over to the Infrastructure Team.

288
00:19:59,824 --> 00:20:03,119
The most important thing right now
is a fast response,

289
00:20:03,202 --> 00:20:04,704
-and also--
-I don't think

290
00:20:04,787 --> 00:20:07,665
we can solve this that way.

291
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:32,732
Let's not make things difficult.

292
00:20:32,815 --> 00:20:35,526
Let's focus on the core issue here.

293
00:20:36,110 --> 00:20:39,822
A famous YouTuber said he was paying
top money for the best internet plan

294
00:20:39,905 --> 00:20:43,868
from Korea's best telecom company,

295
00:20:43,951 --> 00:20:46,454
only to go, "The service was terrible

296
00:20:46,537 --> 00:20:48,706
and not worth what I paid."
So he called us out.

297
00:20:48,789 --> 00:20:50,624
-Yes.
-I've said it again and again.

298
00:20:50,708 --> 00:20:54,086
A direct approach is necessary
in situations like this.

299
00:20:54,170 --> 00:20:56,589
Be open and honest.

300
00:20:56,672 --> 00:20:58,007
You're right, Mr. Kim.

301
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:59,300
The simplest way is

302
00:20:59,383 --> 00:21:01,761
to just admit what happened
and deal with it by the book.

303
00:21:01,844 --> 00:21:02,803
Song-hee.

304
00:21:03,846 --> 00:21:04,930
Yes, Mr. Kim.

305
00:21:05,014 --> 00:21:07,266
Get in touch with the YouTuber
and tell him

306
00:21:07,975 --> 00:21:09,769
to take down all the videos.

307
00:21:13,856 --> 00:21:14,982
Go on.

308
00:21:15,649 --> 00:21:17,610
All the videos. Okay.

309
00:21:19,779 --> 00:21:20,696
All…

310
00:21:21,238 --> 00:21:22,114
A refund?

311
00:21:22,740 --> 00:21:23,741
Yes.

312
00:21:23,824 --> 00:21:25,326
GET A REAL ESTATE LICENSE IN A YEAR

313
00:21:25,409 --> 00:21:26,452
INTENSIVE COURSE INFO SHEET

314
00:21:26,535 --> 00:21:27,536
Okay.

315
00:21:30,331 --> 00:21:31,999
May I ask

316
00:21:32,625 --> 00:21:34,418
