317
00:21:35,044 --> 00:21:37,505
I gave it some thought, and--

318
00:21:37,588 --> 00:21:39,507
Don't lose your confidence.

319
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:42,551
It's the kind of exam
even grandmas can pass.

320
00:21:42,635 --> 00:21:44,929
It's not that I'm not confident--

321
00:21:45,012 --> 00:21:48,140
The one or two million won tuition fee
is not what's important.

322
00:21:48,766 --> 00:21:52,102
You're shaping your next 50 years,
the second phase of your life.

323
00:21:52,978 --> 00:21:54,396
Let me explain.

324
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:55,815
It's not about money.

325
00:21:55,898 --> 00:21:58,818
-Look at them. Tell her.
-They started with no prior knowledge.

326
00:21:58,901 --> 00:22:00,694
And they passed in just six months.

327
00:22:00,778 --> 00:22:01,946
FASTEST EXAM PASSERS

328
00:22:02,029 --> 00:22:05,074
If you pass both exams in one go,
