329
00:22:05,157 --> 00:22:07,743
Look over there. "The 2024 Hall of Fame."

330
00:22:07,827 --> 00:22:09,829
How wonderful is that?

331
00:22:09,912 --> 00:22:12,998
No wonder so many students
enroll at this academy.

332
00:22:13,082 --> 00:22:14,708
-Ma'am.
-Yes.

333
00:22:16,585 --> 00:22:17,795
Let me speak.

334
00:22:32,476 --> 00:22:33,602
What?

335
00:22:33,686 --> 00:22:35,604
You're out. Where are you?

336
00:22:36,105 --> 00:22:37,815
Jongno. On my way back home.

337
00:22:37,898 --> 00:22:40,025
You're nearby.
Do you want to come join us?

338
00:22:40,109 --> 00:22:42,236
-Have you eaten?
-What are you up to?

339
00:22:42,319 --> 00:22:45,406
We're having lunch at Namdaemun Park View.

340
00:22:45,489 --> 00:22:48,617
We can add one more person for free
with our membership.

341
