when will you ever eat at a hotel?

344
00:22:55,374 --> 00:22:59,003
I had dinner with your brother-in-law
at the Hyatt two years ago!

345
00:22:59,628 --> 00:23:01,547
Okay. Good for you.

346
00:23:01,630 --> 00:23:02,590
Come quickly.

347
00:23:02,673 --> 00:23:04,758
Sang-cheol has something to tell you.

348
00:23:05,759 --> 00:23:07,761
Why would your husband
have anything to say to me?

349
00:23:07,845 --> 00:23:08,971
Lure her with the king crabs.

350
00:23:09,054 --> 00:23:10,180
-King crabs?
-Yes.

351
00:23:10,723 --> 00:23:12,892
The king crabs here are holy crabs.

352
00:23:13,642 --> 00:23:16,061
These king crabs are in-crab-ible!

353
00:23:16,145 --> 00:23:18,272
-Come over!
-See you in a bit.

354
00:23:20,774 --> 00:23:22,443
I'll ask for support, and…

355
00:23:22,526 --> 00:23:24,737
That little punk is trying to play me?

356
00:23:27,489 --> 00:23:30,492
You're lucky you have
a team leader like me.

357
00:23:30,576 --> 00:23:32,870
If you take Do Jin-woo's bait
on a day like this,

358
00:23:32,953 --> 00:23:35,915
you'll end up dancing
to Team 2's tune forever.

359
00:23:35,998 --> 00:23:38,125
So, you really think

360
00:23:38,208 --> 00:23:41,170
a YouTuber with two million subscribers

361
00:23:41,253 --> 00:23:43,631
will just take the video down
because we asked?

362
00:23:43,714 --> 00:23:45,341
You think I was born yesterday?

363
00:23:46,300 --> 00:23:47,259
Then?

364
00:23:47,885 --> 00:23:50,346
We're going with a counterattack strategy.

365
00:23:50,429 --> 00:23:52,431
Now's the time to go hard.

366
00:23:52,514 --> 00:23:55,434
Then he'll be like, "What's going on?"

367
00:23:55,517 --> 00:23:59,563
Then we can negotiate
from a more advantageous position.

368
00:23:59,647 --> 00:24:02,274
They don't make nuclear weapons
to actually use them.

369
00:24:03,901 --> 00:24:07,154
We really need to think carefully here.

370
00:24:07,237 --> 00:24:09,323
This might take away
any room left for negotiation.

371
00:24:09,943 --> 00:24:10,824
What do you mean?

372
00:24:10,908 --> 00:24:12,284
Instead of "What's going on?"

373
00:24:12,368 --> 00:24:15,955
