the videos down without even apologizing?"

374
00:24:16,038 --> 00:24:18,040
"Are they insane?"

375
00:24:18,540 --> 00:24:21,168
It might provoke him even more.

376
00:24:21,251 --> 00:24:23,379
Those guys make a living
off ads and sponsorships.

377
00:24:23,462 --> 00:24:25,756
