"IT-BOY" VIDEO DELETION REQUEST
SALES TEAM 1

395
00:25:33,365 --> 00:25:34,366
READ RECEIPT

396
00:25:35,701 --> 00:25:36,660
STATUS: READ

397
00:25:40,831 --> 00:25:43,292
Why did you choose now,
of all times, to be efficient?

398
00:25:44,334 --> 00:25:45,627
You guys too.

399
00:25:45,711 --> 00:25:48,380
You should've stopped me at the meeting
if it was such a bad idea.

400
00:25:48,464 --> 00:25:49,506
I'm sorry.

401
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:52,009
Seriously. You should've
tried harder to stop me.

402
00:25:52,092 --> 00:25:55,304
It's so hard to work with you guys.

403
00:25:56,472 --> 00:25:58,348
My gosh.

404
00:26:01,935 --> 00:26:02,853
Sung-gu.

405
00:26:06,815 --> 00:26:10,611
GENERAL MANAGER KIM NAK-SU

406
00:26:11,445 --> 00:26:13,947
How did your call
with Yangpyeong go this morning?

407
00:26:14,031 --> 00:26:16,408
I begged and pleaded,

408
00:26:16,492 --> 00:26:19,036
so I think we can get away with it.

409
00:26:19,119 --> 00:26:20,120
-Mr. Kim.
-Yes.

410
00:26:20,204 --> 00:26:21,288
Remember, we have…

411
00:26:24,458 --> 00:26:26,710
What do you expect me to do with it?

412
00:26:26,794 --> 00:26:28,170
Go away.

413
00:26:29,296 --> 00:26:30,506
Jeez.

414
00:26:32,925 --> 00:26:35,219
Today's ACT incident
reminded me once again

415
00:26:35,302 --> 00:26:38,514
of just how pathetic the mindset
of major Korean corporations really is.

416
00:26:38,597 --> 00:26:39,807
It's not surprising at all.

417
00:26:39,890 --> 00:26:41,225
So starting now, we--

418
00:26:52,236 --> 00:26:55,280
You guys even have a CEO's office.

419
00:26:56,323 --> 00:26:59,868
With our new Chief Destruction Officer
over there, Kim Su-gyeom,

420
00:26:59,952 --> 00:27:02,204
we'll thoroughly break
all conventional rules.

421
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:03,914
Let's start with that.

422
00:27:04,540 --> 00:27:05,999
Give him a round of applause.

423
00:27:06,083 --> 00:27:08,377
-Welcome.
-Su-geon.

424
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:10,587
-It's Su-gyeom.
-I haven't made up my mind yet.

425
00:27:13,590 --> 00:27:16,677
I still can't quite tell
what kind of company this is,

426
00:27:17,761 --> 00:27:20,556
so let me watch you work a bit
before I make a decision.

427
00:27:26,687 --> 00:27:28,147
Go on.

428
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:34,319
Okay. If that's the case…

429
00:27:34,403 --> 00:27:35,863
What? Let go of me.

430
00:27:36,822 --> 00:27:37,739
Are you sure?

431
00:27:41,743 --> 00:27:42,703
Ta-da!

432
00:27:44,204 --> 00:27:45,247
I'm a pro.

433
00:27:48,458 --> 00:27:52,129
I'll get some more of those king crabs
that my sister loves so much.

434
00:27:52,212 --> 00:27:53,463
Get the legs, will you?

435
00:27:53,547 --> 00:27:55,591
Plenty of legs. Got it.

436
00:27:55,674 --> 00:27:56,925
A lot of them, honey.

437
00:28:05,976 --> 00:28:07,144
So you see,

438
00:28:07,227 --> 00:28:09,813
I'm planning to quit my job

439
00:28:09,897 --> 00:28:12,107
