452
00:28:37,424 --> 00:28:38,508
If Nak-su joins us,

453
00:28:38,592 --> 00:28:40,928
with his experience
at a major telecom company,

454
00:28:42,596 --> 00:28:45,182
it would be like putting wings on a tiger.

455
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:50,520
I actually have a few connections
over at ACT,

456
00:28:50,604 --> 00:28:54,274
