477
00:29:49,871 --> 00:29:51,123
Goodness gracious.

478
00:29:51,206 --> 00:29:53,166
You saw it too, didn't you?

479
00:29:53,250 --> 00:29:55,419
In what world
is that a reasonable response?

480
00:29:55,502 --> 00:29:57,170
That was pathetic.

481
00:29:57,254 --> 00:30:00,173
How can they handle it like that
in this day and age?

482
00:30:00,674 --> 00:30:03,343
Didn't you say you were friends
with that YouTuber?

483
