We're not super close.
He's an acquaintance.

484
00:30:06,930 --> 00:30:08,223
-An acquaintance?
-Yes.

485
00:30:08,307 --> 00:30:09,349
What's going on?

486
00:30:09,433 --> 00:30:11,852
Did something happen
at my husband's company?

487
00:30:11,935 --> 00:30:12,978
You don't know?

488
00:30:13,603 --> 00:30:15,647
