490
00:30:17,316 --> 00:30:18,859
Why should I take down my video?

491
00:30:18,942 --> 00:30:20,694
Why should I? Why?

492
00:30:20,777 --> 00:30:21,820
Gloves are off.

493
00:30:21,903 --> 00:30:23,989
I'll put everything I've got
as IT-BOY on the line

494
00:30:24,072 --> 00:30:25,866
and see this through to the end.

495
00:30:25,949 --> 00:30:28,452
And I just got a report

496
00:30:28,952 --> 00:30:32,205
about a public facility
in Yangpyeong, Gyeonggi Province.

497
00:30:32,289 --> 00:30:35,000
Whether intentionally or not,
ACT went ahead

498
00:30:35,083 --> 00:30:38,086
and forced the completion of construction,

499
00:30:38,170 --> 00:30:41,381
even though Super Giga Internet service
isn't available in the area.

500
00:30:41,465 --> 00:30:43,342
That's corporate abuse.

501
00:30:43,967 --> 00:30:47,346
If you've been affected by this,
let me know.

502
00:30:47,429 --> 00:30:49,139
I'll step up and handle it.

503
00:30:49,222 --> 00:30:51,266
This has been IT-BOY.

504
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:54,061
Support me by liking,
subscribing, and enabling notifications.

